Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How were the members of the\NSpecial Crimes Unit assembled?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to look into a murder from a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I ended up investigating the murder of Professor Odagiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We figured out that neither Kasai, who we thought was the culprit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...nor Nishihori were responsible for Professor Odagiri's murder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The investigation was at a dead end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Officer Kusakabe from the Public Safety Department, who was cooperating with the investigation, suddenly said this:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further and someone is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed Professor Odagiri! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what connection does this case have with the Special Crimes Unit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What secrets lie hidden?{\i0}
