Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The rain stops, there's a break in the clouds{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:02.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The blue sky's calling out to you{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:07.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Alright, it's almost time to head out{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}I don't need anyone else's advice{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}I've gotta trust my own instincts{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:18.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}It's high time I found my own way{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Fire Up, Ignition{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The heavy pressure's on{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Slam the accelerator and power through{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:30.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Surprise, the whole world's got drive!\N{\fs30}(It's faster than ever){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:36.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Feeling high like you're finally awake\N{\fs30}(Show me your Drivin'){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:41.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Once you're on the road to destiny\N{\fs30}(Keep chasin' forever){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:46.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}There's no way to go in reverse...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:49.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}All we need is Drive!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.90,EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,478)\an1\move(1189,620,350,620,23,397)\fs42}Episode 3{\c&H5B42D3&\3c&HDAE3E6&}   Who{\c\3c\be1} killed Professor Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by you killed Professor Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not totally sure though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Kyu, you're getting less and less confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Odagiri took medicine for his \Nheart every day, right? I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down! Put the weapon down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had been helping the Professor with his research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With research, do you mean the Anima System?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly was that research?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A system to upload the human brain into the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.40,Default Top,,0,0,0,,I was giving him advice on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,475)\4a00\fs56\shad3\bord1.6\pos(640,570)\3c&H010100&}April 8th, 2014 (Tuesday)  6:48 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:02.86,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recently...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I'm being watched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know who... but I think someone is after my research.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way! That couldn't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just now! Did you hear something outside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's there?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Professor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that his medicine was in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault! The professor died because I spilled the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Kyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't his medicine in the cup on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He... had a heart condition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since he was so busy with his research, I prepared his medicine every day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After I found out what he'd done to my work...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I prepared a different medicine, one that would put an intense strain on his heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why they didn't find any drugs in his system during the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. It wasn't your fault the Professor died, Kyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You changed your tune quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to ask one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Professor Odagiri talk about anyone called "Banno"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he used to run into Banno a lot during his walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They even met after he died, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Banno was already dead, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he have seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think it could have been a random guy with the same name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If he went any further, Kusakabe's warning would have come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not dig any deeper into this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consider this a warning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any further and someone is going to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His attitude was completely different from when we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we might be closer to the truth than we realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. About the Professor's machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out something new after running a few tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before that you won't die \Neven if you raise the voltage to max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you keep the voltage at max and wear it for more than five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it will be lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If the current continues flowing \Nthrough the body for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will stop blood flowing from the heart, resulting in a condition called ventricular fibrillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So if someone made it so the Professor couldn't remove his helmet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...and kept the assistants busy for five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can commit a murder without leaving any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tomari from the Special Crimes Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you put Kusakabe on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kusakabe is not here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His computer is not at his desk and \Nwe haven't been able to contact him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Professor's estimated time \Nof death is between 7 and 9pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspects are Kasai Hitomi and Nishihori Kouya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kasai is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was caught by a security camera trying to board a bullet train at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Nishihori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he is innocent as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I arrested him a while before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So then who...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I called up the Public Safety Department. Looks like he has suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having them look up what Kusakabe Akira was doing on the night of the Global Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It was the night of the Global Freeze, so people couldn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So how was Professor Odagiri killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Global Freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I increased the voltage on his little invention as high as it would go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I prepared a different medicine, one that would put an intense strain on his heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wear the helmet for more than five minutes it will be lethal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I move?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it. The truth behind the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to all these mysteries lie in the Professor's estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A question for the people watching this on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Professor Odagiri die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have been watching Kamen Rider Drive since episode one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...then you should know the answer already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me give you a huge hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the multiple Secret Mission episodes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...released in the Kamen Rider Drive series so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the type name of every title.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an important hint hidden in those titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, can you solve this mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for Type Tokujo's unraveling quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose the reason why Professor Odagiri died from these options.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Access the Secret Mission website to participate in the quiz!
