Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So the professor died on the same day as the Global Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The data was deleted from the Professor's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We were interested in his contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth behind the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the murderer the Professor's assistant, Kasai Hitomi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the imprisoned convict Nishihori Kouya...{\i0}
