Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.80,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...or the isolated Public Safety officer, Kusakabe Akira?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.22,Default Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit is...
